author: Brie Stimson
title: Guatemala health minister compares US to Wuhan, claims deportations causing spike in coronavirus cases
description: Guatemala’s minister of health reportedly said Tuesday that more than half of deportees from the United States have tested positive for the coronavirus.
content: Guatemala’s minister of health Tuesday said the United States was practically the Wuhan of the region -- referring to the Chinese city at the epicenter of the coronavirus -- while claiming deportees from the U.S. have caused a sharp spike in Guatemalan cases.… [+3561 chars]
